trans-unit.source: Provides qualifying information to a callback method when a <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject.ObjectChanged"></xref> event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Gir kvalifiserte informasjon til en tilbakeringing metode når en <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject.ObjectChanged"> </xref> inntreffer.

trans-unit.source: PeerObjects are run-time data items associated with an application, such as certificates, pictures, avatars, or specific descriptions.
trans-unit.target: PeerObjects er kjøretidsdata elementer som er knyttet til et program, for eksempel sertifikater, bilder, avatarer eller beskrivelser.

trans-unit.source: They may also be referred to as a host peer's registered applications, objects and presence information.
trans-unit.target: De kan også refereres til som et vertsnavn node registrerte programmer, objekter og tilgjengelighetsinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject> is changed, an event is raised.
Calling this method requires a <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState> of <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState>.
This state is created when the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration> session begins.

Gets the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType"></xref> that specifies the type of change that has occurred to a <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.Peer"></xref> or <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType"> </xref> som angir hvilken type endringer som er gjort til en <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.Peer"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Unless specified, the default value for this property is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis angitt, er standardverdien for denne egenskapen `null`.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType"></xref> that specifies the type of change that has occurred.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType"></xref>som angir hvilken type endringer som er gjort.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"></xref> associated with the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"></xref> for which object information has changed.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"> </xref> knyttet til den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"> </xref> for objektet som informasjonen er endret.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"></xref> associated with the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"></xref> on which <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject"></xref> information has changed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"> </xref> knyttet til den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"> </xref> som <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject"> </xref> informasjonen er endret.

trans-unit.source: If the endpoint is not associated with a contact, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> is returned.
trans-unit.target: Hvis endepunktet ikke er knyttet til en kontakt <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> returneres.

trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"> </xref> for objektet som informasjonen er endret.

trans-unit.source: Unless specified, the default value for this property is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis angitt, er standardverdien for denne egenskapen `null`.
